de.upb.t2t.model

Class LoginCredentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.upb.t2t.model.LoginCredentials

  • public class LoginCredentials
extends java.lang.Object
    LoginCredentials are used to verify whether or not a user is allowed to make changes to the online (!) database. They will be sent along with every modification attempt.
    Author:
    Michel May (michel-may@gmx.de)
    See Also:
    OnlineHandler, LoginDialogue
